Paper title: Variation in the global-scale impacts of climate change on crop productivity due to climate model uncertainty and adaptation
GCM(s): CCSM30; CCMA CGCM31; CSIRO mk30; ECHAM5; GFDL CM20; GFDL CM21; GISS MODELEH; GISS MODELER; UKMO HadCM3; UKMO HadGEM; IPSL CM4; CCSR MIROC HI; CCSR MIROC MED; NCAR PCM1
Geog. Scope: Top 15 of producing countries(China, USA, Russia, Germandy, Argentina, Poland, Australia, India, Canada, Ukraine, France, Romania, UK, Hungary, Brazil)
Comments (e.g. Key assumptions): 1. Use of year 2000 harvested area data meant no change in area; 2. Assumed no change to yield via technology improvements.
